 Educational Background



 


Budapest University of Technology & Economics

                  The Budapest University of Technology and Economics is the most significant University of Technology in Hungary and is considered the world's oldest Institute of Technology which has university rank and structure. It was the first institute in Europe to train engineers at university level.It was founded in 1782.

More than 110 departments and institutes operate within the structure of eight faculties. About 1100 lecturers, 400 researchers and other degree holders and numerous invited lecturers and practising expert specialists participate in education and research at the Budapest University of Technology and Economics.                





 Boards & Committees



Corporate Boards ▾




Director

                    2011 - Current                  


PetroVietnam Low Pressure Gas Distribution JSC

                    PetroVietnam Low Pressure Gas Distribution JSC engages in the distribution and transportation of low pressure gas through pipelines. It also trades petroleum, industrial gas, and other oil products, as well as supplies, machineries, and transportation equipment for the oil and gas industries. Its other activities include the provision of technology transfer consultancy services; construction of industrial works, technical infrastructure, and piping systems; real estate business; and mineral exploration activities. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.                  




Director

                    2011 - Current                  


Nui Nho Stone JSC

                    Nui Nho Stone JSC engages in the manufacture and sale of stone and building materials. It produces construction stone and builds Nui Nho and Tan Lap stone quarries. Its other activities include business of real estate, hotels, and restaurants; processing of rubber latex; growing of rubber; and investment of ecological tourism. The company was founded on December 31, 1975 and is headquartered in Binh Duong, Vietnam.                  




Vice Chairman

                    2005 - Current                  


Long An Food Processing Export JSC

                    Long An Food Processing Export JSC engages in manufacture, processing, and trading of agricultural and aquatic products. Its business line include cashew Kernels for export, frozen shrimp for export, and salted cashew nuts. The firm's services also include investing, processing, producing, trading, importing, exporting and providing services in agricultural products, aquatic products, foodstuff, machinery, equipment and materials for production. The company was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Tan An, Vietnam.                  




Independent Director

                    2007 - 2014                  


DHG Pharmaceutical JSC

                    DHG Pharmaceutical JSC engages in the production, sale, and trade of pharmaceutical products. The company's products include pharmaceutical drugs and cosmetics, and dietary supplements. Its activities also involve the import of medicine production equipment; manufacture and export of processed food and cosmetics; and trade, import, and export of materials for veterinary medicine, food for cattle, poultry, and aquatic products. The company was founded on Sep 02, 1974 and is headquartered in Can Tho, Vietnam.                  




Director

                    Prior                  


VTC Telecommunications JSC

                    VTC Telecommunications JSC engages in the design, manufacture, and sale of telecommunications equipment. It provides electronic and telecommunications consulting solutions, and installation and technical services. The company also invests in telecommunication infrastructures. VTC Telecommunications was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.                  





 Other Affiliations




              Song Nhu Nguyen is affiliated with
                            PetroVietnam Low Pressure Gas Distribution JSC, Nui Nho Stone JSC, Long An Food Processing Export JSC, DHG Pharmaceutical JSC, VTC Telecommunications JSC.
            




